18
00:00:12,582 --> 00:00:15,582
http://hiqve.com/

19
00:00:17,606 --> 00:00:19,191
<i>Jedi mystery!</i>

20
00:00:19,274 --> 00:00:22,903
<i>A lightsaber was found
on the moon of Oba Diah,</i>

21
00:00:22,986 --> 00:00:24,696
<i>belonging to Sifo-Dyas,</i>

22
00:00:24,779 --> 00:00:28,950
<i>the Jedi responsible for
the creation of the clone army.</i>

23
00:00:29,034 --> 00:00:31,953
<i>The Jedi have learned
that before the start of the war</i>

24
00:00:32,037 --> 00:00:34,122
<i>Count Dooku murdered Sifo-Dyas</i>

25
00:00:34,206 --> 00:00:38,460
<i>and skillfully manipulated the Republic
into the galactic conflict</i>

26
00:00:38,543 --> 00:00:42,005
<i>intending for the Jedi to fight
with the clones at their side.</i>

27
00:00:43,256 --> 00:00:47,219
<i>Now, as the Jedi Council meets to
discuss the purpose of this deception,</i>

28
00:00:47,302 --> 00:00:51,973
<i>Master Yoda meditates deep into
the Force in search of answers.</i>

29
00:00:57,771 --> 00:00:59,231
<i>Yoda.</i>

30
00:00:59,314 --> 00:01:01,316
Hear you I do.

31
00:01:02,776 --> 00:01:04,444
Who are you?

32
00:01:05,946 --> 00:01:08,073
My imagination it must be.

33
00:01:08,657 --> 00:01:09,950
<i>No.</i>

34
00:01:11,159 --> 00:01:13,995
<i>It is I, Qui-Gon Jinn.</i>

35
00:01:14,287 --> 00:01:17,332
That cannot be. Dead you are.

36
00:01:17,874 --> 00:01:21,419
<i>No. I am part of the living Force, Yoda.</i>

37
00:01:32,681 --> 00:01:34,516
Impossible.

38
00:01:38,103 --> 00:01:42,440
I am not sure this Council is admitting
how grave a situation we are in.

39
00:01:42,524 --> 00:01:43,900
What are you saying?

40
00:01:43,984 --> 00:01:47,946
That Dooku is not the Sith Lord,
merely an apprentice.

41
00:01:48,029 --> 00:01:51,783
That, like many things,
remains unclear.

42
00:01:51,866 --> 00:01:55,287
Master Yoda, your thoughts
on these revelations?

43
00:01:57,706 --> 00:01:59,249
Yes, yes.

44
00:02:00,875 --> 00:02:03,253
Forgive me, deep in thought I was.

45
00:02:08,174 --> 00:02:09,217
You were saying?

46
00:02:10,552 --> 00:02:13,555
Master Ki-Adi-Mundi is worried.

47
00:02:13,763 --> 00:02:16,933
Yes, worried we all should be.

48
00:02:17,475 --> 00:02:19,978
Lies and mistrust surround us
in the Senate

49
00:02:20,061 --> 00:02:23,398
and perhaps even within these walls.

50
00:02:25,150 --> 00:02:28,278
On the precipice we are. Yes.

51
00:02:28,903 --> 00:02:31,865
The growing dark side
endangers us all.

52
00:02:37,329 --> 00:02:38,580
Excuse me, everyone.

53
00:02:38,913 --> 00:02:41,249
Master Kenobi,
may I speak with you in private?

54
00:02:42,083 --> 00:02:43,710
Of course.

55
00:02:53,303 --> 00:02:56,222
There is great turmoil
within Master Yoda.

56
00:02:56,306 --> 00:02:58,350
Yes. We all sensed it.

57
00:02:58,433 --> 00:03:02,395
For something to affect Yoda
this deeply concerns me.

58
00:03:02,604 --> 00:03:05,106
We must keep an eye on our old friend.

59
00:03:05,523 --> 00:03:08,651
The war has taxed all of us to our limit.

60
00:03:08,777 --> 00:03:11,446
I suppose we're just surprised
that Master Yoda has one.

61
00:03:11,613 --> 00:03:13,990
I hope it's that simple.

62
00:03:14,074 --> 00:03:18,536
But I feel the shadow of something
greater on our horizon.

63
00:03:33,301 --> 00:03:34,719
<i>Yoda.</i>

64
00:03:40,308 --> 00:03:43,770
Master Yoda. Sorry,
I didn't see you there.

65
00:03:43,853 --> 00:03:46,231
Is everything okay?

66
00:03:46,314 --> 00:03:49,984
Encountered something difficult I have.

67
00:03:50,068 --> 00:03:53,071
Difficult? For you, Master?

68
00:03:53,154 --> 00:03:56,324
Spoke with Master Qui-Gon Jinn
on Mortis did you not?

69
00:03:57,367 --> 00:04:00,662
Yes, so did Obi-Wan.

70
00:04:00,745 --> 00:04:04,124
However, since he's dead,
we don't think it was actually him.

71
00:04:04,207 --> 00:04:08,336
Rather an illusion. A mind trick
formed out of our memories.

72
00:04:09,212 --> 00:04:11,464
That's what Obi-Wan believes.

73
00:04:12,006 --> 00:04:13,550
Why do you ask?

74
00:04:13,633 --> 00:04:15,927
Perhaps nothing it is.

75
00:04:16,177 --> 00:04:18,430
Everything that we know about
the Force tells us

76
00:04:18,513 --> 00:04:23,351
that an individual retaining their identity
after death is impossible.

77
00:04:23,435 --> 00:04:25,562
Everything that we know, yes.

78
00:04:25,854 --> 00:04:28,857
But what about what we know not?

79
00:04:30,191 --> 00:04:34,779
Master Yoda, are you suggesting that
you have spoken with Master Qui-Gon?

80
00:04:35,196 --> 00:04:37,157
Suggest this I am not.

81
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:40,160
Rest I need. Yes, rest.

82
00:04:41,578 --> 00:04:43,413
Then speak with the Council I shall.

83
00:04:49,085 --> 00:04:52,547
Sense something that I have not before.

84
00:04:52,630 --> 00:04:54,507
Impossible it seems.

85
00:04:54,591 --> 00:04:56,885
Trust my feelings I do not.

86
00:04:58,386 --> 00:05:00,889
The voice I hear
does not come from within,

87
00:05:00,972 --> 00:05:03,475
but speaks from beyond.

88
00:05:04,434 --> 00:05:09,564
Know I must if I am alone,
or if any of you can hear it as well.

89
00:05:09,647 --> 00:05:12,775
Then together we shall meditate.

90
00:05:52,899 --> 00:05:55,443
Hear the voice I did not.

91
00:05:58,071 --> 00:06:00,573
I also sensed nothing.

92
00:06:01,824 --> 00:06:03,910
Answers, we will not find.

93
00:06:04,577 --> 00:06:07,914
Tired I am. Rest I must.

94
00:06:08,414 --> 00:06:12,710
We have to consider that
this may be a deception by the Sith.

95
00:06:12,794 --> 00:06:14,504
Surely you are not suggesting

96
00:06:14,587 --> 00:06:18,258
Master Yoda is susceptible
to such manipulation?

97
00:06:18,341 --> 00:06:23,555
Master Yoda, you are older
and wiser than any living Jedi,

98
00:06:23,638 --> 00:06:27,684
but this does not mean you are beyond
the corruption of the dark side.

99
00:06:28,142 --> 00:06:29,394
Agree I do.

100
00:06:29,477 --> 00:06:32,605
A possibility we must consider it is.

101
00:06:32,689 --> 00:06:36,484
Clouded so much of our vision
the dark side has.

102
00:06:36,568 --> 00:06:39,320
Deceived I may be.

103
00:06:52,250 --> 00:06:55,628
All I can tell you is
I have scanned Master Yoda three times

104
00:06:55,712 --> 00:06:57,505
and I find nothing wrong with him.

105
00:06:57,589 --> 00:06:59,799
I am not an expert on his biology,

106
00:06:59,882 --> 00:07:03,344
but from my point of view,
he is in perfect health.

107
00:07:03,970 --> 00:07:05,763
And his mind?

108
00:07:06,180 --> 00:07:08,683
No signs of any degeneration.

109
00:07:09,350 --> 00:07:12,937
This section of the brain
is particularly active.

110
00:07:13,021 --> 00:07:14,939
More than I have seen in any other Jedi.

111
00:07:15,773 --> 00:07:19,110
Probably what happens when
you approach 900 years old.

112
00:07:19,193 --> 00:07:21,946
I think we are overlooking
an obvious thread.

113
00:07:22,030 --> 00:07:23,406
Which is?

114
00:07:23,489 --> 00:07:25,825
Count Dooku was Yoda's apprentice.

115
00:07:25,908 --> 00:07:28,953
And Count Dooku
has fallen to the dark side.

116
00:07:29,037 --> 00:07:31,748
All of us have apprenticed
to Master Yoda.

117
00:07:31,831 --> 00:07:34,375
He cannot be held accountable
for Dooku's descent.

118
00:07:34,667 --> 00:07:37,462
But they are connected. Profoundly.

119
00:07:37,545 --> 00:07:39,088
Whoever the Sith Lord is,

120
00:07:39,172 --> 00:07:42,800
he may be using this relationship
as a direct link to Yoda.

121
00:07:42,884 --> 00:07:44,010
Impossible.

122
00:07:44,093 --> 00:07:45,803
Are you so sure?

123
00:07:45,887 --> 00:07:49,015
If the Sith Lord wanted to
attack the Jedi Order from within,

124
00:07:49,098 --> 00:07:51,893
Master Yoda would be
the perfect choice.

125
00:07:52,602 --> 00:07:55,229
I fear we are
more vulnerable than we think.

126
00:07:56,564 --> 00:07:58,650
I would like to suggest something.

127
00:07:58,733 --> 00:08:00,693
A deprivation ritual.

128
00:08:00,777 --> 00:08:03,696
It is a dangerous procedure,
but one that will without question

129
00:08:03,780 --> 00:08:06,783
allow Yoda to go to
the source of this voice.

130
00:08:06,991 --> 00:08:09,827
Whatever, whoever it may be.

131
00:08:09,911 --> 00:08:12,497
I am sorry to bother you,
but the Chancellor's requesting

132
00:08:12,580 --> 00:08:15,124
that Master Yoda attend
an emergency meeting.

133
00:08:15,583 --> 00:08:17,043
I will go.

134
00:08:17,126 --> 00:08:18,419
What about the treatment?

135
00:08:18,503 --> 00:08:21,297
Ask Master Yoda what he wants to do.

136
00:08:21,381 --> 00:08:23,424
Only he can decide now.

137
00:08:34,936 --> 00:08:37,146
The chamber works to
deprive the patient

138
00:08:37,230 --> 00:08:39,607
of any stimulation except from within.

139
00:08:39,691 --> 00:08:43,361
Master Yoda will be taken into
an induced meditation.

140
00:08:43,444 --> 00:08:45,154
This allows the patient to go deeper

141
00:08:45,238 --> 00:08:47,532
than anything we can achieve
by ourselves.

142
00:08:47,949 --> 00:08:50,827
Master Yoda, you don't have to do this.

143
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:53,162
Solve this puzzle I will.

144
00:08:53,246 --> 00:08:55,873
But it could be
more dangerous than you realize.

145
00:08:55,957 --> 00:08:58,710
The danger is not to know the truth.

146
00:08:58,793 --> 00:09:00,795
See clearly I must.

147
00:09:01,879 --> 00:09:03,464
Help this will.

148
00:09:12,640 --> 00:09:14,600
Life signs are normal.

149
00:09:15,351 --> 00:09:17,603
Beginning the procedure.

150
00:09:37,623 --> 00:09:38,624
What are you doing?

151
00:09:38,708 --> 00:09:40,418
By reducing the flow of oxygen

152
00:09:40,501 --> 00:09:43,463
the body will be forced
into a deep meditative state.

153
00:09:43,546 --> 00:09:46,632
It will take him
as close to death as possible.

154
00:09:46,716 --> 00:09:47,884
I don't like this.

155
00:09:50,219 --> 00:09:53,514
<i>Yoda, no. This is not the way.</i>

156
00:09:57,268 --> 00:10:01,397
<i>Come to Dagobah.
The answers you seek are here.</i>

157
00:10:03,566 --> 00:10:04,776
But why?

158
00:10:04,859 --> 00:10:07,528
<i>You must complete what I could not.</i>

159
00:10:07,612 --> 00:10:09,530
His vital signs are dropping too low.

160
00:10:09,614 --> 00:10:12,533
-But the test...
-I want him out of there now!

161
00:10:13,367 --> 00:10:16,329
Master Yoda! Master Yoda, wake up!

162
00:10:16,954 --> 00:10:18,372
<i>Come back to us!</i>

163
00:10:18,456 --> 00:10:21,793
<i>Speak of this to no one. Trust no one.</i>

164
00:10:22,251 --> 00:10:24,545
<i>Come to Dagobah, alone!</i>

165
00:10:25,546 --> 00:10:28,508
<i>Master Yoda! Master Yoda, wake up!</i>

166
00:10:34,180 --> 00:10:35,723
Welcome back, old friend.

167
00:10:36,224 --> 00:10:38,226
Thought we lost you there.

168
00:10:38,726 --> 00:10:41,395
Speaking to the dead I was.

169
00:10:41,479 --> 00:10:43,689
Friends long gone.

170
00:10:43,773 --> 00:10:45,733
Good friends.

171
00:10:49,237 --> 00:10:50,655
<i>How did the procedure go?</i>

172
00:10:50,738 --> 00:10:51,739
We're not certain.

173
00:10:52,615 --> 00:10:54,367
Yoda seems to be under the impression

174
00:10:54,450 --> 00:10:57,245
he contacted the dead
and spoke with them.

175
00:10:58,996 --> 00:11:00,998
<i>What are your thoughts
on this, Doctor?</i>

176
00:11:01,082 --> 00:11:03,125
Medically, Yoda seems fine,

177
00:11:03,209 --> 00:11:06,170
but I cannot speak
to his spiritual balance.

178
00:11:06,254 --> 00:11:08,923
What Yoda claims is not possible.

179
00:11:09,006 --> 00:11:10,716
As far as we know.

180
00:11:11,425 --> 00:11:16,013
The dead are part of the Cosmic Force
and lose their individuality.

181
00:11:16,097 --> 00:11:18,808
I fear Yoda is under attack by the Sith,

182
00:11:18,891 --> 00:11:22,019
though how remains unknown to us.

183
00:11:22,103 --> 00:11:24,355
<i>Until what's going on is clear,</i>

184
00:11:24,438 --> 00:11:27,441
<i>I want temple guards
placed in the medical bay.</i>

185
00:11:37,827 --> 00:11:42,039
I'm prescribing nothing but bed rest
for you now, Master Yoda.

186
00:11:44,792 --> 00:11:46,335
I will leave you two alone.

187
00:11:49,964 --> 00:11:51,299
You asked for me, Master?

188
00:11:51,465 --> 00:11:54,302
Yes, friends, we are?

189
00:11:54,385 --> 00:11:55,636
Of course.

190
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:59,265
A choice you must make.
Worried for you I am.

191
00:11:59,473 --> 00:12:01,183
Why is that?

192
00:12:01,267 --> 00:12:04,979
Do something for me you must.
Blamed you will be.

193
00:12:05,730 --> 00:12:08,190
What? What must I do?

194
00:12:08,316 --> 00:12:10,818
Help me to escape. Yes.

195
00:12:10,902 --> 00:12:12,236
Escape?

196
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:13,654
But you're not in prison.

197
00:12:13,738 --> 00:12:16,324
No? Perhaps.

198
00:12:17,450 --> 00:12:19,452
But perhaps I am.

199
00:12:20,995 --> 00:12:23,748
Already, all around us the cage may be.

200
00:12:23,831 --> 00:12:26,542
A journey I must make, alone.

201
00:12:27,627 --> 00:12:31,923
The Council will not want you
to travel at all, alone even less.

202
00:12:32,006 --> 00:12:35,426
Disobeying the Council,
your expertise is,

203
00:12:35,551 --> 00:12:37,511
that is why I ask for your help.

204
00:12:38,179 --> 00:12:42,308
It is the spontaneity you find so easily
which others do not.

205
00:12:42,391 --> 00:12:44,810
That is what sets you apart.

206
00:12:44,894 --> 00:12:48,814
Now, a walk you will take me on.
Come, come.

207
00:12:50,232 --> 00:12:51,901
Where are you going?

208
00:12:52,944 --> 00:12:55,196
Some fresh air I require.

209
00:12:55,905 --> 00:12:59,200
It's okay, he's with me. I'll watch him.

210
00:13:04,330 --> 00:13:06,457
I hope I don't regret this.

211
00:13:17,385 --> 00:13:19,887
Hey, Artoo, I have a mission for you.

212
00:13:20,012 --> 00:13:23,015
Doctor Nema is going to notice
Yoda is missing any minute now.

213
00:13:23,099 --> 00:13:26,102
Get him to his ship as fast as possible
and get him out of here.

214
00:13:44,745 --> 00:13:47,748
Where's Master Yoda?
What have you done?

215
00:13:47,832 --> 00:13:50,209
Hey, for once, none of this was my idea.

216
00:14:44,722 --> 00:14:47,767
Yes, stay with the ship you may.

217
00:14:47,850 --> 00:14:51,145
This task, for me alone it is.

218
00:15:15,002 --> 00:15:16,337
Here I am.

219
00:15:16,420 --> 00:15:20,132
Ready for my next instruction,
Master Qui-Gon.

220
00:15:23,344 --> 00:15:27,306
<i>Yoda, my old friend,
you have come at last.</i>

221
00:15:28,057 --> 00:15:31,310
Qui-Gon Jinn... Really you, it is?

222
00:15:31,393 --> 00:15:32,686
<i>It is.</i>

223
00:15:32,770 --> 00:15:34,355
Losing my mind I am not?

224
00:15:35,356 --> 00:15:37,525
<i>No, my friend. No.</i>

225
00:15:37,691 --> 00:15:40,069
Why have you brought me here?

226
00:15:40,152 --> 00:15:44,240
<i>Follow the light,
the light will be your guide.</i>

227
00:16:05,094 --> 00:16:07,513
Strong this planet is with the Force.

228
00:16:07,596 --> 00:16:10,891
<i>It is one of the purest places
in the galaxy.</i>

229
00:16:16,897 --> 00:16:18,524
How are you here?

230
00:16:18,607 --> 00:16:20,401
<i>I am a manifestation of the Force.</i>

231
00:16:21,360 --> 00:16:24,238
<i>A Force that consists of two parts.</i>

232
00:16:24,363 --> 00:16:26,991
<i>Living beings generate
the Living Force</i>

233
00:16:27,074 --> 00:16:30,578
<i>which in turn powers the well spring
that is the Cosmic Force.</i>

234
00:16:39,086 --> 00:16:41,172
Show yourself, can you?

235
00:16:41,255 --> 00:16:45,217
<i>I cannot. My training was incomplete.</i>

236
00:16:45,301 --> 00:16:47,845
<i>All energy from the living Force,</i>

237
00:16:47,928 --> 00:16:52,433
<i>from all things that have ever lived,
feeds into the Cosmic Force,</i>

238
00:16:52,516 --> 00:16:57,146
<i>binding everything and communicating
to us through the midi-chlorians.</i>

239
00:16:57,271 --> 00:17:00,357
<i>Because of this I can
speak to you now.</i>

240
00:17:00,816 --> 00:17:02,943
See the future, you can?

241
00:17:03,068 --> 00:17:06,530
<i>I exist where there is no future or past.</i>

242
00:17:07,781 --> 00:17:10,409
Know you who the Sith Lord is?

243
00:17:11,118 --> 00:17:15,372
<i>I can only show you a place where
the answers will be revealed to you.</i>

244
00:17:37,811 --> 00:17:39,021
<i>Be wary,</i>

245
00:17:39,188 --> 00:17:44,276
<i>give power to that which you fear
and it will show itself to you.</i>

246
00:18:35,953 --> 00:18:41,000
<i>No, no, no. You will die!</i>

247
00:18:43,043 --> 00:18:44,545
<i>Sidious...</i>

248
00:18:48,215 --> 00:18:49,383
<i>Sidious...</i>

249
00:18:50,259 --> 00:18:51,552
<i>Sidious...</i>

250
00:18:53,721 --> 00:18:57,641
<i>Join me. There is no other way.</i>

251
00:18:59,601 --> 00:19:00,853
No.

252
00:19:30,257 --> 00:19:33,927
<i>Yoda, come back to us. Yoda.</i>

253
00:19:40,434 --> 00:19:43,937
Such darkness. Such evil.

254
00:19:46,190 --> 00:19:47,691
When will this happen?

255
00:19:48,192 --> 00:19:52,154
<i>It is happening right now.
It has always been happening.</i>

256
00:19:52,237 --> 00:19:57,034
<i>With each day the Clone War wages,
evil is growing in its power.</i>

257
00:19:57,117 --> 00:19:58,744
<i>What you felt in the cave</i>

258
00:19:58,827 --> 00:20:02,164
<i>is merely a portion of what
the dark side now holds.</i>

259
00:20:02,956 --> 00:20:04,666
Such power.

260
00:20:05,209 --> 00:20:09,004
Any hope that the Jedi
can prevail, is there?

261
00:20:09,129 --> 00:20:11,465
<i>There is always hope, my friend.</i>

262
00:20:11,548 --> 00:20:14,885
<i>Though it often comes
in forms not looked for.</i>

263
00:20:14,968 --> 00:20:19,431
<i>The key is knowing how to see it
and seizing that opportunity.</i>

264
00:20:19,515 --> 00:20:23,102
<i>I have been tasked
with guiding you forward.</i>

265
00:20:28,190 --> 00:20:32,903
<i>There can be many outcomes.
But your path is clear, Yoda.</i>

266
00:20:32,986 --> 00:20:36,490
<i>You have been chosen,
as I was before you.</i>

267
00:20:36,615 --> 00:20:38,492
For what chosen am I?

268
00:20:39,410 --> 00:20:42,121
<i>You will learn to preserve
your Life Force,</i>

269
00:20:42,204 --> 00:20:44,706
<i>and so, manifest a consciousness</i>

270
00:20:44,790 --> 00:20:48,877
<i>which will allow you to commune
with the living after death.</i>

271
00:20:50,379 --> 00:20:51,630
How?

272
00:20:51,713 --> 00:20:56,135
<i>Dark times are ahead
and forces of light must remain.</i>

273
00:20:56,635 --> 00:20:59,513
<i>This is the path of only a few Jedi.</i>

274
00:21:00,556 --> 00:21:05,018
<i>You will travel to one of the origins
of all life in the galaxy.</i>

275
00:21:05,185 --> 00:21:07,563
This place is where?

276
00:21:07,688 --> 00:21:10,357
<i>The Force will be your guide.</i>

277
00:21:13,193 --> 00:21:14,945
<i>Goodbye, my friend.</i>

278
00:21:20,742 --> 00:21:23,203
Yes, my friend, all right I am.

279
00:21:24,663 --> 00:21:29,042
No, back to Coruscant,
we are not going yet.

280
00:21:30,544 --> 00:21:34,631
Afraid, only begun our long journey has.

281
00:21:34,655 --> 00:21:39,655
http://hiqve.com/

